thread.title: KarenF

author: KarenF
title: KarenF
text: Rented 2015 Thor Chateau 31L. We got a thorough walkthrough of the systems before leaving her. She made pickup and delivery very convenient and she was so friendly and helpful. The unit was very clean and well maintained. Only has 3200 miles on it. We brought our own linens but those can be rented as well. Unit has 2 slideouts and 2 awnings. Very spacious and bed was comfortable!
